assessment.title: M4 WA Part 1 Check for Understanding

material.mattext: A certain machine takes in `Ein` kJ of energy and does `Wout` kJ of work. What is the efficiency of this machine as a percentage?
A certain machine takes in `Ein` kJ of energy, outputs both work and `Qout` kJ of heat through the exhaust. What is the efficiency, as a percentage, of this machine?
A certain machine takes in energy at a rate of `Pin`.0 kW, and outputs work at a rate of `Pout` kW, and also produces heat that is exhausted. At what rate, in kilowatts, is heat exhausted?
A certain machine is `e`% efficient and outputs work at a rate of `Pout`. kW. At what rate, in kilowatts, is heat exhausted from this machine?

A certain machine operating at steady-state produces an output of work at a rate of `Pout` kW, and produces an exhaust of heat at a rate of `RHout` kW. At what rate, in kilowatts, did this machine take in energy?
A certain object undergoes a temperature change of ΔT = `dT` °F. What is this change in temperature in units of °C?
